content:
Using the Asset Conversion Tool, administrators can migrate existing Assets from the Subscription Management (SM) data model to the Revenue Lifecycle Management (RLM) data model. The tool enables continued Asset Management capabilities in RLM for Assets created in SM. 

Where: The Asset Conversion Tool is an open-source tool for Salesforce customers and is publicly available on GitHub.

How: Customers can invoke the tool, specify a list of Asset IDs they want to convert, call the convert function, and debug logs will indicate if the code executed without error.
title: Asset Conversion Tool for Salesforce
